<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1186.95203.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Comparing specimens of Anthidiellum (Ranthidiellum) recently collected from Thailand, and its cleptoparasite A female Anthidiellum ignotum Engel, 2009 (BSRU-AA- 1249) B female paratype of Anthidiellum phuchongense Nalinrachatakan & Warrit, 2021 (BSRU-AB- 0159) C male paratype of cleptoparasite Stelis flavofuscinular Nalinrachatakan & Warrit, 2021 (BSRU-AB- 0156). Scale bar: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/954858" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

